  <body id="s">
    <p>Regulated by reversible phosphorylation of E1<br>
      -Phosphorylation: inactive<br>
      -Dephosphorylation: active</p>
    <p>PDH kinase and PDH phosphorylase are part of mammalian PDH complex<br>
      -Kinase is activated by ATP <br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; High ATP --&gt; phosphorylated PDH --&gt; less
      acetyl-CoA<br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Low ATP --&gt; kinase is less active and phosphorylase
      removes phosphate from PDH --&gt; more acetyl-CoA</p>
